{
  "stem": "1338.6",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I remember I-- talking to my friend.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "She's now in Vancouver, quite prosperous.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We talked about it two years ago when we visited her.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I looked at her eyes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I remembered her eyes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "She was a redhead.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the whole horror of the Holocaust was sort of in a nutshell when she saw me with a mother.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And all of them, without an exception, had no mother, no father, nobody.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I think that that stayed with me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And maybe my quest for normalcy, my pathological quest for normalcy, was helped a lot-- satisfied-- that I found a mother.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Because I wasn't really anymore one of them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I was normal.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I had a mother.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I was aware of it all the time, the rest of my life.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "All right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We went illegally in December '45.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We were shipped to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They caught us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "At that time, there was no Cyprus yet.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "There was no big wave or the second ship that was caught.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And we were taken to a prison next to Haifa for two weeks.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "It wasn't bad.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "It was a camp, a military camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "We lived there in the barracks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And they deducted the certificates.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "They had a quota, you know, for Jews to enter Palestine since 1939-- $1,500 a month.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "So they deducted the-- the quotas, and they gave us legit-- we became legal residents of Palestine.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And we immediately went to a kibbutz, which was a kibbutz where my mother felt very good about because it was formed by primarily Polish and Austrian Jews.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "A lot of Polish spoken.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "A lot of them from my high school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "So she found herself completely at home, very happy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Found a home.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And-- and what spoiled the thing is my ambitions.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
